sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Svelte View)
    participant A as App (Wails Binding)
    participant PM as PlanningManager
    participant PA as PlanAccess

    Note over C,PA: State Verification Pattern (all three views)
    Note over C,PA: Applied after every mutation: create, update, delete, move, archive, restore

    C->>C: Step 1: Optimistic UI update (modify local state immediately)

    C->>A: Step 2: Backend mutation call (e.g. UpdateTask, CreateTheme, SaveDayFocus)
    A->>PM: [mutation method]
    PM->>PA: [persistence method]
    PA-->>PM: result
    PM-->>A: result
    A-->>C: result

    Note over C,PA: Step 3: Verify frontend matches backend

    alt OKRView (verifyThemeState)
        C->>A: GetThemes()
        A->>PM: GetThemes()
        PM->>PA: GetThemes()
        PA-->>PM: []LifeTheme
        PM-->>A: []LifeTheme
        A-->>C: []LifeTheme (backend truth)
        C->>C: checkStateFromData('theme', frontendThemes, backendThemes)
        C->>C: checkStateFromData('objective', flattenObjectives(...))
        C->>C: checkStateFromData('key-result', flattenKeyResults(...))
    else EisenKanView (verifyTaskState)
        C->>A: GetTasks()
        A->>PM: GetTasks()
        PM-->>A: []TaskWithStatus
        A-->>C: []TaskWithStatus (backend truth)
        C->>C: checkFullState('task', frontendTasks, backendTasks)
        C->>C: Compare fields + per-zone ordering
    else CalendarView (verifyCalendarState)
        C->>A: GetYearFocus(year)
        A->>PM: GetYearFocus(year)
        PM-->>A: []DayFocus
        A-->>C: []DayFocus (backend truth)
        C->>C: checkStateFromData('dayFocus', frontendEntries, backendEntries)
    end

    alt No mismatches
        C->>C: Continue normally
    else Mismatch detected
        C->>C: Show ErrorBanner: "Internal state mismatch detected"
        C->>A: LogFrontend('error', mismatchDetails, 'state-check')
        A->>A: slog.Error(message, source, "frontend")
    end
